name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: tpint - Telugu Proverbs In New Tab

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chrome extension to shows telugu proverbs when new tab is opened.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
